channel1
input: Channel.fromPath
output: goes into fastqc, goes into trimmomatic

- 

FASTQC
input: channel1
output: a report (file 1), channel2

TRIMMOMATIC
input: channel1, adapters file
output: goes into channel2, goes into BOWTIE2AlIGN

BOWTIE2_BUILD
input:
genome file
output: goes into BOWTIE2ALIGN

BOWTIE2ALIGN
input: BOWTIE2_BUILD, TRIMMOMATIC
output: into TAGDIR, into SAMTOOLS flagstat

SAMTOOLS_FLAGSTAT
input: BOWTIE2ALIGN
output: into channel2

channel2
input: TRIM, SAMTOOLS_FLAGSTAT, FASTQC
output: MULTIQC

MULTIQC
input: channel2
output: report (file 2)

SAMTOOLS_SORT
input: BOWTIE2ALIGN
output: SAMTOOLS_IDX

SAMTOOLS_IDX
input: SAMTOOLS_SORT
output:BAMCOVERAGE

BAMCOVERAGE
input: SAMTOOLS_IDX
output: channel3, channel4

channel3
input: BAMCOVERAGE
output: into COMPUTEMATRIX

COMPUTEMATRIX:
input:channel3, window file, bed file
output: into PLOTPROFILE

PLOTPROFILE
input: COMPUTEMATRIX
output: file3

channel4
input: BAMCOVERAGE
output: into MULTIBWSUMMARY

MULTIBWSUMMARY
input: channel4
output: PLOTCORRELATION

PLOTCORRELATION
input: MULTIBWSUMMARY
output: file 4

TAGDIR
input: BOWTIE2ALIGN
output: channel 5

channel5
input: TAGDIR
output: FINDPEAKS

FINDPEAKS
input: channel5
output: POS2BED

channel6
input: POS2BED
output: INTERSECT

INTERSECT
input: channel5
output: REMOVE

REMOVE
input: INTERSECT, blacklist file
ouput: into ANNOTATE, FIND_MOTIFS_GENOME

ANNOTATE
input: genome file, gtf file, REMOVE
output: file5

FIND_MOTIFS_GENOME
input: REMOVE
ouput: genome file